    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Older vehicle in fair overall condition with visible age and wear throughout, but still a usable, presentable driver for someone with realistic expectations. Expect cosmetic imperfections inside and out, along with the kind of deferred maintenance or minor issues that are common on an older car in this condition. It is not a mint example, but it could suit a buyer looking for an affordable older vehicle without project-car level problems.",
