    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward value for a buyer seeking affordable transportation or a practical project. It presents as an honest, as-is opportunity with plenty of potential for someone who appreciates a low entry price and room to make it their own. A sensible choice for cost-conscious shoppers looking for accessible ownership.",
