    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation, a project, or a handy runaround. Priced with its condition in mind, it offers a chance to get on the road without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re after something cheap, honest, and worth a look, come check it out.",
      "price": 5400.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Reliable, no-frills driver with solid bones and plenty of life left for the next owner who wants an affordable commuter or weekend project. The powertrain pulls through the rev range well, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels planted enough for daily use. It shows cosmetic wear and age-related flaws consistent with an older vehicle, but it remains a practical, usable car with strong parts-car/project appeal. If you want inexpensive entry into ownership with room to tinker, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Rough around the edges. Solid cheap project or parts car. Priced to sell fast.",
      "price": 5900.0,
