      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is the kind of car that still turns heads for all the right reasons: full of grit, charm, and opportunity. It has that honest, road-worn character that makes every drive feel like a story in progress, and for the right buyer, it\u2019s a chance to own something with real presence without stretching the budget. Whether you\u2019re after a practical runabout, a hands-on project, or simply a vehicle with personality that stands apart from sterile commuter boxes, this one brings a lot of spirit to the table.",
      "price": 6495.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
